
FastFlow has been originally designed by Massimo Torquati 
(<torquati@di.unipi.it> <massimotor@gmail.com>) and 
Marco Aldinucci (<aldinuc@di.unito.it>).

The first version of the FastFlow code has been mainly written by 
Massimo Torquati. Several other people partecipated to the design and 
development. Among them:
- Massimiliano Meneghin (meneghin@di.unipi.it)
- Marco Danelutto (marcod@di.unipi.it)
- Peter Kilpatrick (p.kilpatrick@qub.ac.uk)


